<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-30 16:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1056 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-ECOMMERCE-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      01-30 1223
