Gore in the polls ahead of Tuesday's New Hampshire primary, Bradley
said Sunday ``more explanation'' was needed about Gore's role in
the 1996 Democratic fund-raising scandal, specifically his
controversial visit to a Buddhist temple. (Keith Meyers/The New
York Times )
