Louis Rams head coach Dick Vermeil, is joined by NFL Commissioner
Paul Tagliabue and Rams owner Georgia Frontiere as Vermeil and his
players celebrate their team's 23-16 victory over the Tennessee
Titans in Super Bowl XXXIV, Sunday. In the last minute of the game,
the Rams' defense held off a furious comeback by Tennessee, which
had advanced to the St. Louis 10-yard line with six seconds
remaining. (Barton Silverman/The New York Times)
